        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "weapon",
        "text": "A spraysling is similar to a standard sling but with a wider cup fitted with a thin blade affixed to the cup's edges. When used to make an attack with a specially prepared packet of spray pellets, the razor slices open the packet and the weapon launches a cluster of stinging pellets.",
        "level": 0,
